i think last night was the most fun night i had on this trip.. as usual we went to the euro-youth hostel.. 

as we were leaving the guy we were talking to the other night was on the computer and he joined us (Charley). while we were there we had the watermelon dreams and a beer and a shot of the BAR TENDERS special.. 

little on later a guy walks over and starts talking to us.. really nice kid his name was Kyle and then his hot aussie frined Davis joins us..

kyle bought me this drink called yagger bomb.. its a shot of yaggermister and then a glass of red bull.. you put the shot of yagger inside the galss of red bull and then dink both at the same time.. it was really good.. maybe because i was already trashed... and shit shell broke his glasses.. 

i had a interesting converstaion with Charley and presidents and then he was trying to explain the difference from 1, 2, and 3 degree murder.. i got the 1 and 3 but 2 was confusing as hell...
never knew i could miss something so much...

i miss home so fucking much... today i just felt like crying! my credit card charged me something to london.. why i dont fucking know i didnt even go there!! it took me a good hour to get ahold of them because i cant fucking dial a 1 800 number from this country! the operator keep saying i need a ATT card and no on here knows what they are on the bright side i bought these nice shoes.. they are white and black velcrow... i wanna go home and hang out with alli brenden and vinny.. i think im gonna get me teeth pulled when we get back so i dont need anymore time off of work... only if you knew

im really beganing to miss home.. 
i mean i love it here... munich and venice were my favortie places
and i like barcelona at night and rome was ok... i loved the colessum

i miss talking to my mom i miss her bitching at me...

im thinking about doing a semester as an exchange student probably in venice or munich... i just gotta learn the language.. i think im gonna take the language course at HCC

the only time im not home my dad comes home.. he came home to see the doctor because his his back is fucked up again...

its sad to say but i miss going to work.. see nikki, jackie, andera, berni, claw (carisa) and mostly mike..

we are in barcelona.. its ok here
we took  a overnight train and slept in bunker type things...
we are thinking about going home a week early.. i kinda dont want to but if everyone else is then i kinda have to cause im not going to go around london or germany by myself.. i duno well see..

i plan on coming back but now i know about the prices and how a can of coke is 4.00 

i miss home but i love it here.. its a culture shock..
the people dont ash their cigs... they just let the as fall....
italians were that nice (except for hottie at the cafe in venice)
and they didnt know alot of english..
barcelona is ok... everything looks the same...
i loved munich.. it looked like ybor..

so yesterday was our last day in venice and we met this really hot guy that worked at the cafe!! babe... his hair sucked ass though! today we are in rome and we dont like it very much! we saw the coliseum it was awesome.. i never thought id see it in reality. when we were walking back.. we were crossing the street and i fell flat on my ass!! fucked up my elbow.. me n ness both got hurt... next is shit shell in london! EURO PASSES SUCK ASSHOLE! FUCKERS!!!!!

im sitting in a lil cafe in venice and its fucking awesome...

last night we were sitting down and drinking a lil and then these old guys came up to us and were like OPA OPA it was fucking great!! 

tomorrow we are off to rome|!

sometimes i duno what the fuck happened! my TV blew in my room.. fuck you know its my luck! i was watching some of the movie Monsters.. it seems really good im going to HCC tomorrow to apply so i can start fucking school again... speaking of that. got my report card to day... finished off with a 3.0! and by the way.... J DEPP WON AN AWARD ON THE MTV MOVIE AWARDS...

bought our plane tickets today.. 1,018.35 each
next.. europass
then its time to fly!

tomorrow show- thrusday skipping school and castle- shells car broke down yesterday so ness al and i stayed with her until it worked again... i got into a fight with some skinhead on dale marbry... i cant wiat til tomorrow at 2:40. ♥ hottie @ marathon FUCK

im in homeroom and we have to do a fucking writting thing.. im so sick of school i think im gonna start college in Jan in stead of August.. but someone said that its easier to get into HCC in august.. i duno hopefully its different in college.. ive been working alot.. i get paid today.. well worth it.

So am i excited about my journal? it took forever to figure out and put it together... i kinda cheated but whatever.. im not completely done let alone satisfied with it.. i need a icon thingy and a background picture but im not exactly sure on how to do the two...

thanksgiving was good.. i worked from 7-2.. talk about being packed! HOLY SHIT! it kinda died down around 12:30.. i found out that this guy at work whom i think is pretty hot is 26!! FUCKING HELL! hes way to old for me.. i would never date someone that is older than me by 2-3 years!26.. gezz i cant get over it! i work the rest of the week.. bummer.. ness said that shed come and see me tomorrow on my break..we got this new manager and hes a complete dick wad! he didnt say a single thing to any of the cashiers.. some chick said that he isnt social.. but dude if your going to work in a business where you deal with people all the time,get a little character! im gonna miss jerry.. him and i didnt start off to well but we are now just starting to get along.i went to my cousins house for the dinner.. it was good..i left around 4:30 i wanted to do my economics project but i ended up playing nintendo and fixing my lg.

i talked to my dad today.. he said its pretty cold and rainy up in the hick town! he may or may or may not come home for a couple of days before hes shipped off again but this time to the Carolinas... then in April he may go to the Virgin Islands...lucky ass!as long as hes home for my graduation in fine!i never knew how much id miss him.. i kinda regret that he took the job but it was something he wanted to do...

saturday night was great.. we went to jess's and brenden's and snorted some shit! i was pretty fucked but you know.. 
my moms dying my hair today hopefully.. i cant wait til its longer so i can color it the way i want to.. i want the bottom half a dark blond and then the top half a mocha color.. im gonna go n see nessa on her break at panara and shells leaving tomorrow to go to kentucky to see her dad for the holiday!

im sitting in the library in mr drewitz class and supposed to be working on a project.. but screw it... my english teacher had something go wrong with her and now we have a sub and all the guys thinks shes hot... i guess thats immature 17 year olds!!

i went to panara last night to see nessa on her break... it was cool it was nice with the weather being as cold as it was...it made me realize how much i hate my fucking job.. the people are rude and the employees that are higher than you just walk all over you.. i cant wait to work somewhere everyone is equal!!

we got only 10 days left before christmas break after we come back from the thanksgiving break... im excited.. im probably going to go and see my dad in arkansas or the carolinas if he transfers.. he got a lab top so it will be easier to talk to him.. 

im confused on how to make my journal look all sassy and stuff.. hopefully alli will help me get it set up soon.. my cell phone bill was 80 bucks and i felt really bad cause i called costumer service cause i thought that they were double charging me and i was reallly rude to the lady but as it turns out i found out what was going on... my bad!

well well thanks to my good pal alli i have a lj account!

school was like normal... dull! i just cant wait to get out of there and start something new.. i got my progress report and surprisingly i did ok..i just realized that highschool is pathetic...but then again college will be the same cause everyone and their mother are going to HCC.. i kinda wanna go to college outta state so i can try something new but i wont anyone...

my dads outta town until january and i really miss him.. i think that the only good thing that has come out of this situation is that my mom and i have became a tad bit closer.. we dont fight as much and she isnt nagging on me a hole lot.. i think i began to relize that she isnt as bad as i protruded her to be... i still keep thinking that every time i walk through the front do that my dads gonna be sitting in the living room....this paycheck i wanna get a new tounge ring but i kind of wanna wait until it healed a lil more...

im going to see shell on her break today and im waiting for allie and ness to call to see if they can hang out..
